Insider Activity


Individual




Lyron L. Bentovim



Mr. Lyron L. Bentovim is Independent Director at Manhattan Bridge Capital, Inc. and Chief Operating & Financial Officer at Top Image Systems Ltd. He is on the Board of Directors at Manhattan Bridge Capital, Inc.
Mr. Bentovim was previously employed as COO, CFO & Head-Investor Relations by Sunrise Telecom, Inc., President & Director by Three-Five Systems, Inc., President & Chief Operating Officer by WebBrix, Inc., Senior Engagement Manager by Mitchell Madison Group LLC, Senior Engagement Manager by USWeb, Chief Financial Officer by NITHealth, a Managing Director by SKIRITAI Capital LLC, and Senior Engagement Manager by McKinsey & Co., Inc. He also served on the board at RTW, Inc., Ault, Inc., and Argonaut Technologies, Inc.
He received his graduate degree from The Hebrew University of Jerusalem and an MBA from the Yale School of Management.



