Insider Activity


Individual




Lyron L. Bentovim



Mr. Lyron L. Bentovim is President & Chief Executive Officer at The Glimpse Group, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Blue Sphere Corp., Manhattan Bridge Capital, Inc. and eGistics, Inc. Mr. Bentovim was previously employed as Chief Operating Officer by Top Image Systems Ltd., COO, CFO & Head-Investor Relations by Sunrise Telecom, Inc., President & Director by Three-Five Systems, Inc., President & Chief Operating Officer by WebBrix, Inc., Senior Engagement Manager by Mitchell Madison Group LLC, Senior Engagement Manager by USWeb/CKS Corp., Senior Engagement Manager by McKinsey & Co., Inc., Chief Financial Officer by NITHealth, and a Managing Director by SKIRITAI Capital LLC. He also served on the board at RTW, Inc., Ault, Inc. and Argonaut Technologies, Inc. He received his graduate degree from The Hebrew University of Jerusalem and an MBA from Yale School of Management.



